OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ford is to invest hundreds of millions 
OL,6, of pounds in its Halewood plant on     
OL,7, Merseyside, helping safeguard 500 jobs.
OL,9,FThe factory will be Ford's first       
OL,10,FEuropean plant to produce components   
OL,11,Ffor electric cars.                     
OL,13,FThe investment will mean the plant will
OL,14,Frun for many years longer, said Stuart 
OL,15,FRowley, president, Ford of Europe.     
OL,17,FThere had been speculation about the   
OL,18,Ffuture of the Halewood factory complex 
OL,19,Fas Ford moves towards electrifying its 
OL,20,Fvehicles.                              
